de_dust war story:
 After dust 2 bombing was a succes, terrorists have decided to bomb the counter-terrorists supply base in the far deserts secretly. The counter-terrorists  saw the situation and immediatly call a backup and ready up for a war with terrorists.

A free roam map that is dust themed


If you encounter any bugs, then pls inform me by typing in the chat
